{"tid":845911,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【20萬剛需？】黃遠輝：估計居屋有20萬份申請","createTime":"2018-10-03T04:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T08:03:54.000Z","uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f865de30d76dde7db2fb12933bcebce634a509f","tid":845911,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"新居屋經52折減價後，今日正式接受申請，連同上期申請名單合併計算，房委會資助房屋小組委員會主席黃遠輝估計，會有20萬份申請表。<br />\n<br />\n黃遠輝今日出席電台節目時表示，有估算今次新申請表連同上期的申請表，合共有20萬份申請表。他表示，明白社會希望多些資助房屋，但在調整公私營房屋比例時要小心考慮，可能會影響目前20萬名劏房及板間房住戶會捱貴租，因此在增加房屋供應時，不能忽略這些家庭的需要。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181003/58750500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58750500&d=Aow8GF3K3lDdrXZekHQXT8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ced9eec8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58750500&h=7756bfc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181003/58750500</a>"},{"pid":"c9257ae53053eafe6484548d3193853a057c9ad1","tid":845911,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T05:06:31.000Z","msg":"20萬即係同你講 唔會抽中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91f43a989c7207b63b80d8a87fe7d783ae4dae9","tid":845911,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"即係樓價如果跌一半就會有二十萬成交？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749e5fe5f0a8ea9b7bb0b474a4b540c90b4d32d3","tid":845911,"uid":40089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f91f43a989c7207b63b80d8a87fe7d783ae4dae9","tid":845911,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"即係樓價如果跌一半就會有二十萬成交？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201